dx": 2839, "end_char_idx": 3103, "metadata_seperator": "\n", "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, "19172ee6-1e58-44ad-a233-43fbe1afe748": {"__data__": {"id_": "19172ee6-1e58-44ad-a233-43fbe1afe748", "embedding": null, "metadata": {}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "424431dd-1a80-4784-951c-811424449e25", "node_type": "4", "metadata": {}, "hash": "67b246d883013447e15333556f19aeb8a43e9f0d8ca86e00ce7eab45ef195776", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "2": {"node_id": "59a2d0ff-19fb-4905-bbe5-0e1c541ae5a7", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "449df750b01759a03868f00203d074028df9bb2abc3b03e24834ecdb2ce62e62", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "3": {"node_id": "f54ec7d2-39ba-44db-9cea-f91339acc603", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "9e1bb89e6aead17296465c69bbf4f6d887214f5362356eb421ae980614f1fcb9", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}}, "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_separator": "\n", "text": "1 The Buyer records that it is (and/or has been and/or will be) partaking in investigations of (and/or negotiations with) various Seller/s and/or Business/es, with a view towards potentially acquiring such Business/es. The Buyer further acknowledges that it is serious in its investigations towards potentially acquiring a Business.", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 3105, "end_char_idx": 3437, "metadata_seperator": "\n", "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, "f54ec7d2-39ba-44db-9cea-f91339acc603": {"__data__": {"id_": "f54ec7d2-39ba-44db-9cea-f91339acc603", "embedding": null, "metadata": {}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "424431dd-1a80-4784-951c-811424449e25", "node_type": "4", "metadata": {}, "hash": "67b246d883013447e15333556f19aeb8a43e9f0d8ca86e00ce7eab45ef195776", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "2": {"node_id": "19172ee6-1e58-44ad-a233-43fbe1afe748", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "926d6a9432e5fab5911ba4a54d34dc9e747fbca1f2121d92029a9206f3e1782c", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "3": {"node_id": "95f3122c-edde-4bb9-98b3-526bfca3a293", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "04b065cacbdd3bea21a87fad1461281c3c53aff39a5ea97535838ff9296b9e82", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}}, "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_separator": "\n", "text": "2.2 The Buyer realises that,\n\n in the course of its investigations (and/or negotiations), Aldes, the Business/es and/or the Seller/s will be required to disclose  Confidential  Information  and/or  Confidential  Material  to  the  Buyer,  albeit  for  the  purposes  of  assisting  the  Buyer  in  determining whether or not it wishes to acquire any Business/es or otherwise.", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 3439, "end_char_idx": 3814, "metadata_seperator": "\n", "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, "95f3122c-edde-4bb9-98b3-526bfca3a293": {"__data__": {"id_": "95f3122c-edde-4bb9-98b3-526bfca3a293", "embedding": null, "metadata": {}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "424431dd-1a80-4784-951c-811424449e25", "node_type": "4", "metadata": {}, "hash": "67b246d883013447e15333556f19aeb8a43e9f0d8ca86e00ce7eab45ef195776", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "2": {"node_id": "f54ec7d2-39ba-44db-9cea-f91339acc603", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "9e1bb89e6aead17296465c69bbf4f6d887214f5362356eb421ae980614f1fcb9", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "3": {"node_id": "99b7814b-4f5c-427a-b16c-64921b44c4e6", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "c621e55f8d7da36a4a456204cae249298483af4d21d5e5b3a7d023113c5bd2fa", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}}, "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_separator": "\n", "text": "2.3 The  Buyer  acknowledges and agrees that  the  sole  reason for,\n\n  and  the  sole  purpose  of,  any  disclosures of  Confidential  Information  and/or Confidential Material by Aldes, the Business/es and/or the Seller/s is strictly limited to that stated in clauses 2.1 and 2.2 above (the \u201c Purpose \u201d).\n\n3.", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 3816, "end_char_idx": 4127, "metadata_seperator": "\n", "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, "99b7814b-4f5c-427a-b16c-64921b44c4e6": {"__data__": {"id_": "99b7814b-4f5c-427a-b16c-64921b44c4e6", "embedding": null, "metadata": {}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "424431dd-1a80-4784-951c-811424449e25", "node_type": "4", "metadata": {}, "hash": "67b246d883013447e15333556f19aeb8a43e9f0d8ca86e00ce7eab45ef195776", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "2": {"node_id": "95f3122c-edde-4bb9-98b3-526bfca3a293", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "04b065cacbdd3bea21a87fad1461281c3c53aff39a5ea97535838ff9296b9e82", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "3": {"node_id": "5646f277-8511-4c42-8ded-4cae3d145563", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "e71eab81f29495d82e16c030203aaeff398818c8da30977245d4213d2bdda854", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}}, "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_separator": "\n", "text": "PERIOD\n\n3.1 This Agreement shall be taken to have commenced, notwithstanding the signature date hereof,\n\n on the earliest of:\n\n3.1.1 the date of signature of this agreement by the Buyer; or\n\n3.1.\n\n2 the date of the first meeting or correspondence between Aldes and the Buyer regarding any Business/es and/or Seller/s; and shall continue in perpetuity thereafter.\n\n4. UNDERTAKING OF CONFIDENTIALITY\n\n4.", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 4128, "end_char_idx": 4529, "metadata_seperator": "\n", "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, "5646f277-8511-4c42-8ded-4cae3d145563": {"__data__": {"id_": "5646f277-8511-4c42-8ded-4cae3d145563", "embedding": null, "metadata": {}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "424431dd-1a80-4784-951c-811424449e25", "node_type": "4", "metadata": {}, "hash": "67b246d883013447e15333556f19aeb8a43e9f0d8ca86e00ce7eab45ef195776", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "2": {"node_id": "99b7814b-4f5c-427a-b16c-64921b44c4e6", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "c621e55f8d7da36a4a456204cae249298483af4d21d5e5b3a7d023113c5bd2fa", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "3": {"node_id": "a6c5ed7d-9457-4552-a795-11d93a56fccc", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "59274d9a822cf4560266889b94a932d177eecd258b17ce3a5083b450d0c5bf7f", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}}, "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_separator": "\n", "text": "1 The Buyer undertakes, towards and in favour of each of Aldes,\n\n the Business/es and the Seller/s (jointly and severally), with regard to and in respect of any and all of the Confidential Information and/or Confidential Materials, that it will  keep same (irrespective of how same was disclosed to the Buyer) strictly confidential and secret and that it will hold same in absolute trust and confidence.", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 4529, "end_char_idx": 4932, "metadata_seperator": "\n", "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, "a6c5ed7d-9457-4552-a795-11d93a56fccc": {"__data__": {"id_": "a6c5ed7d-9457-4552-a795-11d93a56fccc", "embedding": null, "metadata": {}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "424431dd-1a80-4784-951c-811424449e25", "node_type": "4", "metadata": {}, "hash": "67b246d883013447e15333556f19aeb8a43e9f0d8ca86e00ce7eab45ef195776", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "2": {"node_id": "5646f277-8511-4c42-8ded-4cae3d145563", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "e71eab81f29495d82e16c030203aaeff398818c8da30977245d4213d2bdda854", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "3": {"node_id": "c4acdd31-2c93-42fe-a8e6-56752bf15cf0", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "bb12896c15167f7c86e7ec4b297e33f2c384b875a8b78105720ed2db3a6ce589", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}}, "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_separator": "\n", "text": "Initial\n_______________\n\nBUYER\u2019S CONFIDENTIALITY AND NON-DISCLOSURE AGREEMENT\n\n4.\n\n2 The Seller/s and/or the Business/es shall retain ownership of all their Confidential Information and/or Confidential Materials, which shall be deemed to be lent to the Buyer for the Purpose only.\n\n5.", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 4932, "end_char_idx": 5216, "metadata_seperator": "\n", "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, "c4acdd31-2c93-42fe-a8e6-56752bf15cf0": {"__data__": {"id_": "c4acdd31-2c93-42fe-a8e6-56752bf15cf0", "embedding": null, "metadata": {}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "424431dd-1a80-4784-951c-811424449e25", "node_type": "4", "metadata": {}, "hash": "67b246d883013447e15333556f19aeb8a43e9f0d8ca86e00ce7eab45ef195776", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "2": {"node_id": "a6c5ed7d-9457-4552-a795-11d93a56fccc", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "59274d9a822cf4560266889b94a932d177eecd258b17ce3a5083b450d0c5bf7f", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "3": {"node_id": "0dbfa2af-651b-4d6b-b64b-775f5c2056aa", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "bde6b9e23c9f2246b6b3a0550273e8b3f0e54bd6c478973a86074476687b61f6", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}}, "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_separator": "\n", "text": "LIABILITY\n\n5.1 The  Buyer  acknowledges  that  it  will  be  liable,\n\n  responsible  and  accountable  to  each  of  Aldes,  the  Business/es  and  the  Seller/s  (jointly  and severally) for a breach of this Agreement by itself or any of its related or inter related parties, employees, consultants, advisers and/or agents.\n\n6. NON-CIRCUMVENT\n\n6.", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 5217, "end_char_idx": 5564, "metadata_seperator": "\n", "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, "0dbfa2af-651b-4d6b-b64b-775f5c2056aa": {"__data__": {"id_": "0dbfa2af-651b-4d6b-b64b-775f5c2056aa", "embedding": null, "metadata": {}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "424431dd-1a80-4784-951c-811424449e25", "node_type": "4", "metadata": {}, "hash": "67b246d883013447e15333556f19aeb8a43e9f0d8ca86e00ce7eab45ef195776", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "2": {"node_id": "c4acdd31-2c93-42fe-a8e6-56752bf15cf0", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "bb12896c15167f7c86e7ec4b297e33f2c384b875a8b78105720ed2db3a6ce589", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "3": {"node_id": "fdf013ce-7e66-4ce9-9926-a804da6e416f", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "0f3ed0e393daaff5952de8543e3a78facc17f7bf0de8feb3f4d32a86b26ba3a4", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}}, "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_separator": "\n", "text": "1 The Buyer acknowledges that Aldes will be deemed and regarded (and will be) the effective cause of any transaction which may  transpire and/or materialise between the Buyer and any Business/es and/or Seller/s.\n\n6.", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 5566, "end_char_idx": 5781, "metadata_seperator": "\n", "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, "fdf013ce-7e66-4ce9-9926-a804da6e416f": {"__data__": {"id_": "fdf013ce-7e66-4ce9-9926-a804da6e416f", "embedding": null, "metadata": {}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "424431dd-1a80-4784-951c-811424449e25", "node_type": "4", "metadata": {}, "hash": "67b246d883013447e15333556f19aeb8a43e9f0d8ca86e00ce7eab45ef195776", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "2": {"node_id": "0dbfa2af-651b-4d6b-b64b-775f5c2056aa", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "bde6b9e23c9f2246b6b3a0550273e8b3f0e54bd6c478973a86074476687b61f6", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "3": {"node_id": "94fbd0d7-365b-4b19-ab51-9031bb3ff3c6", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "fa997c264f6bb3cce4fc790fdfee3b42db1b3e4592d332d513350d200919109e", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}}, "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_separator": "\n", "text": "2 The Buyer warrants and guarantees that it will never circumvent Aldes (albeit directly itself or indirectly through any of its subsidiaries, holding companies,  group  companies,  related  parties  and/or  inter-related  parties  or  otherwise  indirectly),  in  negotiating  or  concluding  any transactions,  arrangements  and/or  agreements contemplated in clauses  2.1  and/or  2.", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 5783, "end_char_idx": 6169, "metadata_seperator": "\n", "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, "94fbd0d7-365b-4b19-ab51-9031bb3ff3c6": {"__data__": {"id_": "94fbd0d7-365b-4b19-ab51-9031bb3ff3c6", "embedding": null, "metadata": {}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "424431dd-1a80-4784-951c-811424449e25", "node_type": "4", "metadata": {}, "hash": "67b246d883013447e15333556f19aeb8a43e9f0d8ca86e00ce7eab45ef195776", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "2": {"node_id": "fdf013ce-7e66-4ce9-9926-a804da6e416f", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "0f3ed0e393daaff5952de8543e3a78facc17f7bf0de8feb3f4d32a86b26ba3a4", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "3": {"node_id": "f9c8c737-0bc2-42fa-bb9d-5ec15e3af88d", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "cd14cb783d24362fe686e905d03d32e6dc8f77ca37bb12d985d477c1f821d5eb", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}}, "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_separator": "\n", "text": "2  above  with (or  with regard to)  any  Seller/s and/or Business/es. For avoidance of doubt, the Buyer will at all times act in good faith and will only transact and deal with Seller/s and/or Business/es, via the brokerage, intervention and mediation of Aldes.\n\n6.3 The Buyer acknowledges and agrees that Aldes is,", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 6171, "end_char_idx": 6487, "metadata_seperator": "\n", "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, "f9c8c737-0bc2-42fa-bb9d-5ec15e3af88d": {"__data__": {"id_": "f9c8c737-0bc2-42fa-bb9d-5ec15e3af88d", "embedding": null, "metadata": {}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "424431dd-1a80-4784-951c-811424449e25", "node_type": "4", "metadata": {}, "hash": "67b246d883013447e15333556f19aeb8a43e9f0d8ca86e00ce7eab45ef195776", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "2": {"node_id": "94fbd0d7-365b-4b19-ab51-9031bb3ff3c6", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "fa997c264f6bb3cce4fc790fdfee3b42db1b3e4592d332d513350d200919109e", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "3": {"node_id": "c17d47eb-267b-4a8a-a358-105d2d7d238f", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "36f98705f6a0f072450f8f62d49bc2dff1077c23d51b790fc15806695f4e4b6f", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}}, "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_separator": "\n", "text": "will be and will remain entitled to receipt of its agreed brokerage commission (albeit due and payable by the Seller/s, the Business/es, the Buyer or any of them), should the Buyer (albeit directly itself or indirectly through any of its subsidiaries, holding companies, group companies, related parties and/or inter-related parties or otherwise indirectly) or anyone else the Buyer may have introduced to the Business/es and/or Seller/s, conclude any agreements and/or transactions contemplated in clauses 2.", "m