ussions with the Buyer) is, in part, based on the information presented by the Buyer under and in terms of the Buyer\u2019s Profile on the face of this Agreement.", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 7534, "end_char_idx": 7845, "metadata_seperator": "\n", "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, "6423d19a-9081-4a06-af61-578964d273b0": {"__data__": {"id_": "6423d19a-9081-4a06-af61-578964d273b0", "embedding": null, "metadata": {}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "424431dd-1a80-4784-951c-811424449e25", "node_type": "4", "metadata": {}, "hash": "67b246d883013447e15333556f19aeb8a43e9f0d8ca86e00ce7eab45ef195776", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "2": {"node_id": "264c92e0-b246-4ae4-898a-4c45cb9ba5df", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "36cef0b9421b1aed26302c7bcbe51f7fe651237220ba6304392340c9c09ae405", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "3": {"node_id": "c9bd4701-a1b4-46d3-bf6a-8bc1401b6c9d", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "387c18851f5c6951113c372981e451f9f9e89817cdb6b8e93c2291a8fb7b6956", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}}, "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_separator": "\n", "text": "As such, the Buyer warrants and guarantees that all information presented and provided via and in terms of the Buyer\u2019s Profile  was,  is  and  will  remain  true,  complete  and  accurate  and  that  it  will  immediately  inform  Aldes  should  there  be  any  change  in  the information provided/presented.\n\n9.", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 7848, "end_char_idx": 8161, "metadata_seperator": "\n", "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, "c9bd4701-a1b4-46d3-bf6a-8bc1401b6c9d": {"__data__": {"id_": "c9bd4701-a1b4-46d3-bf6a-8bc1401b6c9d", "embedding": null, "metadata": {}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships":