"}}, "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_separator": "\n", "text": "Should the Buyer fail and/or refuse to enter into and conclude such further agreements, Aldes may, in its sole and absolute discretion, refuse to disclose further information to the Buyer regarding any and/or all Seller/s and/or Business/es.\n\n9.\n\n2 It is noted and agreed that the Buyer and certain of the Seller/s and/or Business/es may from time to time enter into and conclude one or more confidentiality and/or non-disclosure agreements amongst, by and between themselves.", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 8458, "end_char_idx": 8934, "metadata_seperator": "\n", "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, "0934576c-bffa-4341-beeb-181eebddb6be": {"__data__": {"id_": "0934576c-bffa-4341-beeb-181eebddb6be", "embedding": null, "metadata": {}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "424431dd-1a80-4784-951c-811424449e25", "node_type": "4", "metadata": {}, "hash": "67b246d883013447e15333556f19aeb8a43e9f0d8ca86e00ce7eab45ef195776", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "2": {"node_id": "59d08bf6-45d8-4bfb-ad0f-900d247bd25a", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "5c3b73c9b20d8c9b1daea607914a3c5bc8ffb3a1e38ea7f23a1e702968e834ca", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "3": {"node_id": "6cb0c1b8-8ab8-41a9-9f2f-396b55ef2037", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "96f3d49a60f19b1cff23135ada30d0528807c1fc1f8a7acbc3dff08f2d1b3764", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}}, "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_separator": "\n", "text": "It is noted and agreed that those agreements will be in addition to, and not in substitution of/for, this Agreement.", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 8935, "end_char_idx": 9051, "metadata_seperator": "\n", "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, "6cb0c1b8-8ab8-41a9-9f2f-39